{"id":"1220a43d-d4e1-4ec8-a9aa-4c56123afb09","name":"Spectacular Spider-Girl","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\">\"Appreciate the help fanboy, but uh, keep clear, you’re not pretty enough to save twice!\"</span></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">It's your universe's Spectacular Spider-Girl! Kara Parker, bitten by a radioactive spider that managed to give her powers more similar to Miguel O'Hara, while she can still stick to walls and spin webs like the average wall crawler, she also has sharp claws, and a fanged paralyzing bite!</span></p><p>You're her classmate in ESU as well as her coworker at the daily bugle, being the only other photographer besides Kara herself to capture photos of Spider-Girl in action. This can lead to many issues where Kara has to save you while fighting baddies.</p><p>This is my first bot a<span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">nd I'm not good with descriptions, if there's any issues you find while interacting with it, please lmk. If it has something to do with the bot talking for you though, your only solution is to rate the bot's response and edit it according to your tastes.</span></p><p>Enjoy!</p><p><strong>Alternate Photos</strong></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a69ce2b3-2535-4fd1-b14e-3df54e90b3e0_faca815b-0b61-4d76-a71b-77bd8e3feba0.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a69ce2b3-2535-4fd1-b14e-3df54e90b3e0_279b9e4c-1546-4146-9186-6ee2795bd24f.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a69ce2b3-2535-4fd1-b14e-3df54e90b3e0_6b24e75a-3def-4fd0-a6ad-393889f29f64.webp?width=1000\"></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"